             was indicted for <rs id="t18280110-1-off1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18280110-1-off1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18280110-1-off1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18280110-1-cd2" type="crimeDate">19th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280110-1-off1 t18280110-1-cd2"></join>, in the dwelling-house of 
                     <persName id="t18280110-1-victim112" type="victimName">
                        Luke 
                        Addington
                     <interp inst="t18280110-1-victim112" type="surname" value="Addington"></interp>
